JoyXY wasd deadzone 40 # Strafe
CamXY Mouse 100 # Used to counter recoil
mousecalibration 20000
ingamemouse 5
mousepriority flick # Disable normal camera motion while using wheel
ActionWheelXY flick # Action wheel for quick turning
flickdeadzone 40

PinkyLeft V # Weapon Special
