Right 4 # Potion

MenuL Tab # Weapon List
MenuR Escape # Pause

ActionH 1 # Melee
ActionV 2 # Ranged

ActionA Space # Jump / Dodge
ActionB E # Use

ActionC 5 # Wield Grenade
ActionD T # Tag / Social Wheel
